## Any other business

Robert Brockway noted that there had been extensive discussions on SPI
allowing payments via PayPal directly.  Several board members observed that
we would need a separate bank account for PayPal and someone pointed out
that opening a bank account for this purpose was approved in resolution
[2013-12-12.mcs.1](/corporate/resolutions/2013/2013-12-12.mcs.1).  SPI
treasurer Michael Schultheiss agreed to open an account soon.


